<span id="freeTextContainer3648409534167816232">This was more novella length. I hadn&apos;t realized that. I try to avoid novellas.<br/><br/>This was definitely a different kind of romance--older people, heavy on the first wife overtones. <br/><br/>There were some errors (like grammar, punctuation) that need attention. That is often the case with Indie publications.<br/><br/>This was LDS fiction.<br/><br/>Nice story. Nice to read something different now and then.</span>
  <span id="freeText3648409534167816232" style="display:none">This was more novella length. I hadn't realized that. I try to avoid novellas.<br /><br />This was definitely a different kind of romance--older people, heavy on the first wife overtones. <br /><br />There were some errors (like grammar, punctuation) that need attention. That is often the case with Indie publications.<br /><br />This was LDS fiction.<br /><br />Nice story. Nice to read something different now and then.</span>
